Hello!

We are writing to let you know that the **Claude 3.5 Sonnet** model will be=
 **deprecated in Windsurf on October 22, 2025**. After this date, the model=
 will no longer be available for use in the platform.

This change follows Anthropic=E2=80=99s official deprecation timeline for C=
laude 3.5 Sonnet ([see announcement here](https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/a=
bout-claude/model-deprecations#2025-08-13%3A-claude-sonnet-3-5-models)).

**What this means for you**:

=C2=A0


- Any chats with Cascade or inline Commands using **Claude 3.5 Sonnet** wil=
l stop working after **October 22, 2025**.=20
- We recommend migrating to **Sonnet 4.5** or one of the other Claude model=
s currently available in Windsurf for continued access to Anthropic=E2=80=
=99s most capable offerings.=20
We appreciate your understanding and thank you for continuing to build with=
 Windsurf.

Best,
The Windsurf Team


900 Villa St, 94041, Mountain View

This email was sent to=C2=A0liencf@gmail.com

You've received it because you've subscribed to our newsletter.

